.col-lg-6
  .main-box.clearfix
    header.main-box-header.clearfix
      h2 Dismissible alerts with links
    .main-box-body.clearfix
      .alert.alert-success.fade.in
        button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='alert', type='button') ×
        i.fa.fa-check-circle.fa-fw.fa-lg
        strong Well done!
        |  You successfully read this important alert message.
      .alert.alert-info.fade.in
        button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='alert', type='button') ×
        i.fa.fa-info-circle.fa-fw.fa-lg
        strong Heads up!
        |  This alert needs your attention, but it's not super important.
      .alert.alert-warning.fade.in
        button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='alert', type='button') ×
        i.fa.fa-warning.fa-fw.fa-lg
        strong Warning!
        |  Best check yo self, you're not looking too good.
      .alert.alert-danger.fade.in
        button.close(aria-hidden='true', data-dismiss='alert', type='button') ×
        i.fa.fa-times-circle.fa-fw.fa-lg
        strong Oh snap!
        |  Change a few things up and 
        a.alert-link(href='#') try submitting again
        | .
